title: The (almost) complete works of J. D. Salinger (mobi, epub)
description:
The (almost) complete works of J. D. Salinger, available in mobi and epub formats: 

The Catcher in the Rye
Franny and Zooey
Hapworth 16, 1924
Nine Stories
Raise High the Roof Beam, Carpenters
Seymour: An Introduction
Uncollected Stories:
    The Young Folks (1940)
    Go See Eddie (1940)
    The Hang of It (1941)
    The Heart of a Broken Story	(1941)
    The Long Debut of Lois Taggett (1942)
    Personal Notes of an Infantryman (1942)
    The Varioni Brothers (1943)
    Both Parties Concerned (1944)
    Soft-Boiled Sergeant (1944)
    Last Day of the Last Furlough (1944)
    Once a week Won't Kill You (1944)
    Elaine (1945)
    A Boy in France (1945)
    The Sandwich Has No Mayonnaise (1945)
    The Stranger (1945)
    I'm Crazy (1945)
    Slight Rebellion off Madison (1946)
    A Young Girl in 1941 with No Waist at All (1947)
    The Inverted Forest	(1947)
    A Girl I Knew (1948)
    Blue Melody	(1948)
